WEBVTT

00:10.667 --> 00:11.865
<i> PREVIOUSLY ON "GREENLEAF"...</i>

00:11.867 --> 00:12.932
I DON'T TRUST YOU
ANYMORE.

00:12.934 --> 00:14.198
WHAT?

00:14.200 --> 00:15.798
I DON'T KNOW HOW I'M
GONNA EVER TRUST YOU AGAIN.

00:15.800 --> 00:17.999
BISHOP GREENLEAF!

00:18.001 --> 00:20.232
ONE WEEK BEFORE MAE'S BIG DAY.
YOU READY?

00:20.234 --> 00:22.032
HOW DO YOU PREPARE
FOR SUCH A THING?

00:22.034 --> 00:23.832
YOU'RE REALLY MAKIN'
A LOT OF MISTAKES LATELY.

00:24.767 --> 00:26.299
WHO THE HELL IS THIS?

00:26.301 --> 00:27.765
Basie:
BROTHER GREENLEAF.

00:27.767 --> 00:29.565
WHAT HAPPENED
WITH YOU AND TASHA?

00:29.567 --> 00:32.065
ONE KISS. ONE!

00:32.067 --> 00:34.099
ARE YOU DARRELL JAMES'
DAUGHTER?

00:34.101 --> 00:35.732
I AM.

00:35.734 --> 00:36.865
I'M SORRY.
THEY WON'T LISTEN.

00:36.867 --> 00:37.832
WHO WON'T LISTEN?!

00:37.834 --> 00:38.699
FBI.
FBI?

00:38.701 --> 00:39.898
YES, MA'AM.
PLEASE STEP ASIDE.

00:39.900 --> 00:40.965
YOU JUST STOP
RIGHT THERE.

00:40.967 --> 00:42.265
WE HAVE A SEARCH-AND-SEIZURE
WARRANT, MA'AM.

00:42.267 --> 00:45.598
JACOB TRANSFERRED
$200,000 OF CHURCH FUNDS

00:45.600 --> 00:48.298
INTO WHAT TURNED OUT TO BE
A PERSONAL ACCOUNT,

00:48.300 --> 00:50.132
AND THEN YOU,
BISHOP GREENLEAF --

00:50.134 --> 00:52.765
SO THEY THINK --
WITHDREW ALL THOSE FUNDS

00:52.767 --> 00:55.265
AND USED THAT
TO PAY OFF THE I.R.S.

00:55.267 --> 00:57.498
I'VE CALLED AN EMERGENCY MEETING
OF THE DEACON BOARD

00:57.500 --> 00:59.365
TO DISCUSS
YOUR REMOVAL.

00:59.367 --> 01:01.598
YOU CAME?
WHAT DO YOU WANT, LIONEL?

01:01.600 --> 01:02.998
I WANT TO TALK
ABOUT MY DAUGHTER.

01:03.000 --> 01:05.232
MY FATHER PASSED AWAY
THIS AFTERNOON.

01:05.234 --> 01:06.499
ANYTHING I CAN DO
FOR YOU?

01:06.501 --> 01:09.298
YEAH. MAYBE...SIT DOWN
FOR A MINUTE.

01:09.300 --> 01:10.265
IS LIONEL MY FATHER?

01:12.167 --> 01:13.565
I DON'T KNOW.

01:13.567 --> 01:22.265
♪♪

01:22.267 --> 01:23.632
WAIT.

01:23.634 --> 01:25.232
WAIT!

01:28.000 --> 01:30.032
IS LIONEL
MY FATHER OR NOT?

01:34.934 --> 01:37.465
I TOLD YOU I DON'T KNOW.

01:37.467 --> 01:40.198
DO YOU INTEND
ON USING THIS AGAINST ME?

01:40.200 --> 01:41.532
DO YOU?

01:41.534 --> 01:44.365
BECAUSE IF YOU DO,
DO IT NOW.

01:44.367 --> 01:46.699
JUST SCREAM IT
DOWN THE HALLS
OF THE CHURCH.

01:46.701 --> 01:50.165
GO ON, GRACE.
DO IT AND SAVE ME.

01:50.167 --> 01:52.232
JUST SAVE ME
FROM MOUNTING THIS CIRCUS

01:52.234 --> 01:53.565
IN THE SHADOW
OF THE SHAME

01:53.567 --> 01:55.198
THAT YOUR FATHER'S
BROUGHT DOWN ON US ALL.

01:55.200 --> 01:56.932
PLEASE,<i> PLEASE</i>
JUST DO IT NOW.

01:56.934 --> 01:59.798
I WOULD NEVER DO THAT,
MAMA.

01:59.800 --> 02:00.932
YOU KNOW THAT.

02:02.667 --> 02:03.832
THEN, PLEASE...

02:06.467 --> 02:08.398
PLEASE, GRACE...

02:08.400 --> 02:11.899
I<i> NEVER</i> WANT TO SPEAK
ABOUT THIS AGAIN.

02:13.233 --> 02:14.099
PLEASE.

02:18.700 --> 02:20.232
Oh, God...

02:20.234 --> 02:33.398
♪♪

02:33.400 --> 02:35.165
♪ AMEN ♪

02:37.734 --> 02:38.998
♪ ALL RIGHT ♪

02:39.000 --> 02:40.198
♪ AMEN ♪

02:40.200 --> 02:43.398
♪ UH-HUH, HMM ♪

02:43.400 --> 02:45.699
♪ OOH-OOH, OOH ♪

02:48.867 --> 02:50.165
♪ WELL ♪

02:53.667 --> 02:56.598
♪ OH-OHH, OHH ♪

02:56.600 --> 03:02.132
♪ OOH, OOH, OOH, OOH ♪

03:02.134 --> 03:05.132
♪ AMEN, AMEN ♪
♪ OH ♪

03:08.667 --> 03:10.465
♪ YEAH ♪

03:10.467 --> 03:13.465
