 www.vitac.com

03:13.467 --> 03:16.332
CAPTIONS PAID FOR BY
DISCOVERY COMMUNICATIONS

03:20.400 --> 03:21.932
[ DOG BARKING ]

03:23.600 --> 03:24.532
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

03:24.534 --> 03:25.932
VOICEMAIL AGAIN.

03:25.934 --> 03:27.132
[ ICE CLINKING ]
LOOK.

03:27.134 --> 03:29.398
STOP CALLING BASIE
AND JUST CALL TASHA.

03:29.400 --> 03:31.232
LOOK. DON'T YOU UNDERSTAND
HE HAS HER PHONE?!

03:33.100 --> 03:35.432
ARE YOU MORE WORRIED
ABOUT HER OR US?

03:35.434 --> 03:37.031
WHICH DO YOU THINK,
KERISSA?

03:37.033 --> 03:38.098
I DON'T KNOW.

03:38.100 --> 03:39.498
WELL, WHY ASK
SOMETHING LIKE THAT?

03:39.500 --> 03:41.265
BECAUSE I DON'T KNOW!

03:41.267 --> 03:42.865
EVER SINCE YOU
CAME HOME LAST NIGHT

03:42.867 --> 03:44.665
FROM SEEING BASIE...

03:44.667 --> 03:46.598
BUT I HAVEN'T SEEN YOU
LIKE THIS SINCE ZORA GOT STUNG

03:46.600 --> 03:48.465
BY THAT BEE,
AND HER THROAT CLOSED UP.

03:48.467 --> 03:50.532
I'M WORRIED ABOUT US,
OKAY?

03:50.534 --> 03:53.299
US<i> AND</i> TASHA.
[ SCOFFS ] YOU KNOW WHAT?

03:53.301 --> 03:55.032
IF YOU HEARD THE WAY
BASIE WAS TALKING,

03:55.034 --> 03:56.598
YOU'D BE WORRIED, TOO.
TRUST ME.

03:56.600 --> 03:57.765
I THINK
IT'S MOSTLY HER.

03:57.767 --> 03:59.098
AND WHY
WOULD YOU SAY THAT?

03:59.100 --> 04:00.198
BECAUSE THE ONE THING
YOU HAVEN'T DONE

04:00.200 --> 04:02.532
SINCE YOU CAME HOME LAST NIGHT
IS HUG<i> ME...</i>

04:03.867 --> 04:06.065
...AND TELL ME WE'RE NOT
GONNA LOSE OUR CHURCH

04:06.067 --> 04:07.332
OR OUR HOME.

04:07.334 --> 04:09.198
ALL RIGHT.
AND ZORA IS GONE!

04:09.200 --> 04:11.132
COME HERE.
AND -- NO.

04:11.134 --> 04:13.699
LOOK AT OUR LIFE, JACOB.
IT'S RUINED!

04:16.267 --> 04:17.232
WHERE YOU GOING?

04:18.600 --> 04:19.999
BASIE AND TASHA'S.

04:20.001 --> 04:21.831
YOU ALREADY SAID
SHE COULDN'T HELP YOU, JACOB.

04:21.833 --> 04:25.165
LOOK. THAT'S BECAUSE HE'S
TELLING HER TO SAY THAT.

04:25.167 --> 04:26.799
AND WHAT IF
YOU CHANGE HER MIND?

04:26.801 --> 04:27.965
THEN WHAT? HUH?

04:27.967 --> 04:30.699
SHE LOVES YOU, JACOB.
WHERE DOES THAT LEAVE ME?

04:32.800 --> 04:34.932
TASHA IS OUR ONLY WAY
OUT OF THIS,

04:34.934 --> 04:37.598
IF SHE TELLS HER STORY
TO THE FBI.

04:37.600 --> 04:39.199
I GOTTA DO SOMETHING.

04:41.467 --> 04:43.065
[ DOOR OPENS ]

04:43.067 --> 04:46.499
OH, I WISH YOU COULD HAVE
SEEN THAT OLD MAN'S FACE.

04:46.501 --> 04:49.598
I THINK HE HALF BELIEVES
HE REALLY<i> DID</i> HIT THIS.

04:49.600 --> 04:51.865
I DON'T WANT TO
HEAR ANYMORE.

04:51.867 --> 04:53.431
WELL, I GUESS YOU GOT
A HEARING PROBLEM

04:53.433 --> 04:55.165
BECAUSE I AIN'T NEARLY DONE
TALKIN' ABOUT IT.

04:55.167 --> 04:57.698
WE GOT TO GET
OUT OF HERE.

04:57.700 --> 04:58.698
WHY?
WHAT'S UP, BABY?

04:58.700 --> 04:59.765
JACOB'S GOING
TO EVENTUALLY

04:59.767 --> 05:01.632
COME FOR HIS
LITTLE SIDE PIECE, RIGHT?

05:01.634 --> 05:02.832
WHAT MAKES YOU
THINK THAT?

05:02.834 --> 05:04.765
SHE'S ALL THAT'S
BETWEEN HIM AND JAIL.

05:04.767 --> 05:06.798
COME ON.
MOVE YOUR ASS, RO.

05:06.800 --> 05:07.932
WELL, I'M
NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

05:07.934 --> 05:10.199
YES, YOU ARE!
COME ON!

05:10.201 --> 05:11.499
NO.

05:11.501 --> 05:13.465
YOUR HUSBAND SAID
GET UP!

05:13.467 --> 05:14.465
OW!

05:14.467 --> 05:16.265
DON'T BE LIKE THAT,
RO.

05:16.267 --> 05:19.765
LOOK. WHY DON'T Y'ALL
JUST LEAVE ME HERE?

05:19.767 --> 05:21.865
I'M NOT GONNA TELL ANYONE.
I PROMISE.

05:21.867 --> 05:23.132
HERE'S THE PROBLEM
WITH THAT, TASH.

05:23.134 --> 05:24.332
I DON'T TRUST YOU
ANYMORE.

05:25.267 --> 05:26.398
IT'S SAD.

05:26.400 --> 05:27.765
RO, DO ME A FAVOR.

05:27.767 --> 05:30.465
PACK HER BAG UP AND MEET ME
AT THAT MOTEL BY THE RACEWAY,

05:30.467 --> 05:32.265
AND WHERE'S THE
MONEY YOU SAID YOU
WERE GONNA GIVE ME

05:32.267 --> 05:34.099
WHEN WE TALKED ON THE PHONE?
IT'S RIGHT HERE.

05:41.800 --> 05:43.465
WHERE DID THAT MONEY
COME FROM?

05:43.467 --> 05:44.765
NONE OF YOUR
DAMN BUSINESS.

05:44.767 --> 05:46.932
IS THAT THE MONEY
BISHOP GAVE YOU,

05:46.934 --> 05:48.865
THE MONEY YOU WERE SUPPOSED
TO INVEST FOR HIM?!

05:48.867 --> 05:50.265
TASH, WHEN RO SAYS
IT'S NONE OF YOUR BUSINESS,

05:50.267 --> 05:51.331
IT'S FOR
YOUR OWN DAMN GOOD.

05:51.333 --> 05:52.665
NOW GO PACK YOUR BAGS.

05:52.667 --> 05:54.465
[ SIGHS ]

05:54.467 --> 05:56.131
BAS, YOU'RE GONNA NEED
TO USE THAT MONEY

05:56.133 --> 05:57.265
FOR THE BOOKIES IN NEWPORT.

05:57.267 --> 05:58.865
NO, I AIN'T PAYIN'
NOBODY NOTHIN'.

05:58.867 --> 06:00.332
LOOK. THAT WAS A PART
OF THE PLAN. THAT'S --

06:00.334 --> 06:01.599
THIS IS WHAT WE GONNA
LIVE ON, RO --

06:01.601 --> 06:02.865
ME, TASHA, AND YOU

06:02.867 --> 06:05.265
ONCE WE CROSS THAT
OLD LITTLE BORDER TO MEXICO.

06:06.867 --> 06:07.965
HOW THAT SOUND,
BABY?

06:09.467 --> 06:11.332
I KNOW I'VE BEEN GONE.
I GET IT.

06:11.334 --> 06:13.198
I'M GONNA BUY US
A CAR,

06:13.200 --> 06:16.099
CLOTHES, A BOTTLE
OR TWO.

06:19.267 --> 06:20.232
I'LL SEE YOU SOON...

06:22.267 --> 06:23.965
THAT PLACE
BY THE RACEWAY.

06:23.967 --> 06:25.065
WE'LL BE THERE.

06:28.201 --> 06:29.865
[ DOOR CLOSES ]
NOW GO PACK YOUR BAG

06:29.867 --> 06:31.998
UNLESS YOU WANT
ME TO DO IT.

06:32.000 --> 06:34.265
[ Clenching teeth ]
GIRL, GET YOUR ASS OVER THERE!

06:34.267 --> 06:42.465
♪♪

06:42.467 --> 06:43.998
Maxine:
HAVE YOU TALKED
TO GRACE YET?

06:44.000 --> 06:46.132
WELL, YES.
I DID.

06:46.134 --> 06:47.998
GIRL, I'M
SO PROUD OF YOU.

06:48.000 --> 06:50.265
SHE CAME TO<i> ME</i>
WITH IT, ACTUALLY.

06:50.267 --> 06:52.265
AND HOW DID SHE
FIND OUT?

06:52.267 --> 06:55.565
APPARENTLY,
LIONEL TOLD HIS SON.

06:55.567 --> 06:56.965
SO WHAT'S
THE<i> GOOD</i> NEWS?

06:56.967 --> 06:58.032
ARE YOU FEELING BETTER

06:58.034 --> 06:59.499
NOW THAT IT'S
OUT IN THE OPEN?

07:01.400 --> 07:03.932
OH, WHAT IF
SHE TELLS JAMES?

07:03.934 --> 07:05.598
WHAT'S THAT OLD SINNER
GONNA DO,

07:05.600 --> 07:08.532
STAND OUTSIDE
WITH A CLOWN-FROWN FACE

07:08.534 --> 07:11.132
AND A SIGN THAT SAYS,
"SHE'S AS BAD AS ME"?

07:11.134 --> 07:15.065
[ LAUGHING ]
AH, I DON'T THINK SO.

07:15.067 --> 07:16.598
OH.

07:16.600 --> 07:20.532
OH, MAXINE, I'M GONNA
MISS YOU SO<i> MUCH.</i>

07:20.534 --> 07:23.131
YOU'RE GONNA BE FINE,
PASTOR.

07:23.133 --> 07:28.931
♪♪

07:28.933 --> 07:29.865
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

07:32.334 --> 07:33.665
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

07:33.667 --> 07:35.398
HELLO?
GRACE: Hey.

07:35.400 --> 07:37.798
It's your, um,
maybe half-sister.

07:37.800 --> 07:39.865
Oh. Hey.

07:39.867 --> 07:41.998
YOU GOT A SECOND?
Yeah.

07:42.000 --> 07:43.798
Everything okay?

07:43.800 --> 07:48.598
YEAH. I WAS...WONDERING
WHAT YOU THOUGHT OF THE IDEA

07:48.600 --> 07:49.732
OF...

07:49.734 --> 07:52.198
MAYBE TAKING
A BLOOD TEST...

07:52.200 --> 07:53.465
JUST TO BE SURE.

07:53.467 --> 07:55.165
TELL ME WHERE TO BE.

07:55.167 --> 07:56.665
YOU HAVEN'T TOLD KEVIN,
HAVE YOU?

07:59.367 --> 08:00.765
NO.

08:00.767 --> 08:02.432
GOOD.
[ SIGHS ]

08:02.434 --> 08:05.198
SO, UM, LATER TODAY?

08:05.200 --> 08:07.265
WHENEVER, WHEREVER.

08:07.267 --> 08:09.398
Thank you, Aaron.
I'll call you.

08:09.400 --> 08:10.765
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

08:14.800 --> 08:16.065
SO WHO WAS THAT?

08:16.067 --> 08:22.132
♪♪

08:22.134 --> 08:23.265
TASHA.

08:23.267 --> 08:29.998
♪♪

08:30.000 --> 08:30.999
TASHA!

08:32.534 --> 08:33.998
TASHA!

08:34.000 --> 08:46.332
♪♪

08:46.334 --> 08:47.598
Elliot:
THIS ISN'T EASY TO SAY,

08:47.600 --> 08:49.265
BUT I THINK
IT'S YOUR BEST BET,

08:49.267 --> 08:50.865
GIVEN THE FACT
THAT THE U.S. ATTORNEY

08:50.867 --> 08:53.332
MIGHT BE FILING CHARGES
LATER THIS WEEK.

08:53.334 --> 08:55.198
AND WHAT CHARGES
SPECIFICALLY?

08:55.200 --> 08:57.132
BANK FRAUD, WIRE FRAUD.

08:57.134 --> 08:58.165
AND JACOB?

08:58.167 --> 08:59.965
THE SAME,
BUT YOU HAVE A DEFENSE

08:59.967 --> 09:01.365
YOUR SON DOESN'T HAVE,
BISHOP.

09:02.700 --> 09:05.165
THAT'S COLD COMFORT,
BUT TELL ME.

09:05.167 --> 09:07.232
COGNITIVE DYSFUNCTION.

09:08.267 --> 09:09.998
YOU MEAN
I'D SAY I'M SENILE?

09:10.000 --> 09:12.532
THERE ARE CASES WHERE
IT'S WORKED IN THE PAST.

09:12.534 --> 09:13.998
HOW CAN I HOPE
TO RUN THIS CHURCH

09:14.000 --> 09:14.998
IF I PUBLICLY CLAIM

09:15.000 --> 09:16.532
THAT I'M
MENTALLY INCOMPETENT?

09:16.534 --> 09:18.499
DADDY, WE'RE JUST TRYING
TO KEEP YOU OUT OF JAIL.

09:18.501 --> 09:19.765
WHAT --
AFTER THIS SUNDAY...

09:19.767 --> 09:21.032
YOUR MOTHER'S
LITTLE FESTIVAL?

09:21.034 --> 09:23.032
WELL, AFTER THAT,
GIGI, SHE'S GONE.

09:23.034 --> 09:26.332
NOW, I CAN'T HAVE THESE PEOPLE
THINKING THAT I'M LOSING IT.

09:26.334 --> 09:28.465
THE DEACONS ARE
GUNNING AFTER ME AS IT IS,

09:28.467 --> 09:29.798
BUT THANK YOU, THOUGH.

09:29.800 --> 09:31.932
UH, IF YOU TWO
WILL EXCUSE ME,

09:31.934 --> 09:33.665
I HAVE A BAPTISM
TO PERFORM,

09:33.667 --> 09:35.598
AND YOU'LL NOTICE

09:35.600 --> 09:38.632
THAT I'M NOT CARRYING
MY BOOK OF PRAYER.

09:38.634 --> 09:41.365
THAT'S BECAUSE I'VE GOT
THE WHOLE SERVICE...

09:41.367 --> 09:42.365
UP HERE.

09:43.867 --> 09:46.265
YOU COULD GO TO JAIL,
BISHOP,

09:46.267 --> 09:47.732
FOR YEARS.

09:47.734 --> 09:49.465
THAT'S A VERY
REAL POSSIBILITY.

09:49.467 --> 09:50.865
SON...

09:50.867 --> 09:52.732
MY CONCERN OVER THIS
IS KEEPING MY CHURCH,

09:52.734 --> 09:54.398
NOT LOSING IT
TO MY EX-WIFE,

09:54.400 --> 09:55.598
AND I'M...

09:55.600 --> 09:57.731
I'M FAIRLY CERTAIN
I WON'T BE GOING TO JAIL.

09:58.800 --> 10:00.365
[ SCOFFS ]
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

10:02.701 --> 10:03.965
THE OTHER NIGHT,
ELLIOT --

10:03.967 --> 10:06.465
AND I'M...I'M SURE
YOU'LL SCOFF AT THIS...

10:07.900 --> 10:09.632
THE LORD GAVE ME A --

10:09.634 --> 10:12.665
A VISION INTO
THE LAST MOMENT OF MY LIFE.

10:12.667 --> 10:14.198
NOW, IT --

10:14.200 --> 10:16.265
IT WASN'T
NOTHIN' SPECIFIC,

10:16.267 --> 10:18.532
BUT LET'S JUST SAY...
[CHUCKLES]

10:18.534 --> 10:20.099
...IT WASN'T A PRISON.

10:21.133 --> 10:22.165
WHAT WAS IT?

10:23.134 --> 10:25.198
DO YOU BELIEVE
IN VISIONS?

10:25.200 --> 10:26.965
NOW, BE HONEST
BECAUSE GOD'S LISTENIN'.

10:28.201 --> 10:29.232
I'M NOT SURE.

10:31.200 --> 10:32.865
THEN I CAN'T TELL YOU...

10:32.867 --> 10:34.665
BECAUSE YOU WOULDN'T
BELIEVE ME ANYWAY.

10:36.534 --> 10:38.165
ELLIOT.
BISHOP.

10:41.000 --> 10:41.965
[ DOOR OPENS ]

10:43.934 --> 10:45.532
SO THE ONLY WAY
TO KEEP HIM OUT OF JAIL

10:45.534 --> 10:48.065
IS THAT WE HAVE
TO TURN TASHA SKANKS.

10:48.067 --> 10:49.432
I DON'T SEE
ANY OTHER WAY.

10:56.367 --> 10:57.898
THANKS FOR DOING THIS,
AARON.

10:57.900 --> 10:59.432
OF COURSE.

10:59.434 --> 11:01.865
IT'S BETTER FOR ALL OF US
TO KNOW THE TRUTH, RIGHT?

11:01.867 --> 11:03.899
[ LAUGHS ]

11:05.200 --> 11:06.198
WHAT'S SO FUNNY?

11:06.200 --> 11:07.732
I JUST...

11:07.734 --> 11:10.165
[ SIGHS ] OH.

11:10.167 --> 11:11.498
JUST HOW RARELY
I HEAR THAT,

11:11.500 --> 11:13.232
CONSIDERING I WORK
AT A CHURCH.

11:15.400 --> 11:16.831
SUCH IS LIFE, HUH?

11:16.833 --> 11:18.532
YEAH.
SPEAKING OF WHICH...

11:20.367 --> 11:22.565
YOU TOLD KEVIN.
I HAD TO.

11:22.567 --> 11:24.398
HE ASKED WHY WE'VE BEEN
TALKING SO MUCH LATELY.

11:24.400 --> 11:26.332
WILL YOU AT LEAST WAIT
TO TALK TO CHARITY

11:26.334 --> 11:27.932
UNTIL WE KNOW FOR SURE?
TOTALLY.

11:27.934 --> 11:29.332
I JUST --
I WANT TO BE ABLE TO MANAGE

11:29.334 --> 11:31.631
HOW MY FATHER FINDS OUT,
IF THIS IS TRUE.

11:31.633 --> 11:33.365
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]
HE WON'T TELL A SOUL.

11:33.367 --> 11:35.131
OH.

11:35.133 --> 11:36.665
CALL ME
WHEN YOU HEAR BACK?

11:36.667 --> 11:37.932
YOU'LL BE
THE FIRST ONE I TELL.

11:37.934 --> 11:38.998
ALL RIGHT.

11:39.000 --> 11:39.998
THANK YOU.

11:40.000 --> 11:41.532
[ RINGING CONTINUES ]

11:41.534 --> 11:42.799
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

11:43.934 --> 11:44.932
JACOB?

11:44.934 --> 11:46.532
SORRY.
I WAS IN A MEETING.

11:46.534 --> 11:48.198
[ SIGHS ]

11:48.200 --> 11:49.665
I SWEAR...

11:49.667 --> 11:52.065
IF WE CAN HOLD ONTO THIS CHURCH
THROUGH ALL THIS MESS,

11:52.067 --> 11:53.598
it'll be a miracle.

11:53.600 --> 11:55.398
WERE YOU ABLE
TO REACH TASHA?

11:55.400 --> 11:57.265
NO. I HAVEN'T.
[ SIGHS ]

11:57.267 --> 11:59.265
I did go by her house
this morning.

11:59.267 --> 12:00.532
Nobody was there.

12:00.534 --> 12:03.465
AND FROM THE LOOKS
OF THE PLACE,

12:03.467 --> 12:04.632
NOBODY'S COMING BACK.

12:07.667 --> 12:09.065
ISAIAH.

12:09.067 --> 12:10.631
I'M BUSY.

12:10.633 --> 12:12.165
COME LOOK AT THIS
TOUR PROMO I CUT.

12:13.401 --> 12:16.199
[ SIGHS ] PIPE DOWN.
IT'S ALWAYS ABOUT YOU.

12:16.201 --> 12:17.465
OKAY, SO...

12:17.467 --> 12:20.131
I USED A BUNCH OF OLD CLIPS
FROM YOUR PAST SHOWS,

12:20.133 --> 12:23.131
AND THEN I WAS<i> THINKING</i>
WE COULD PLAY A TINY BIT

12:23.133 --> 12:24.131
OF "GOD STEP OVER IT",

12:24.133 --> 12:27.265
BUT WITH THE REMIX
WITH LECRAE...

12:27.267 --> 12:29.265
AND I THINK IT'LL
MAKE IT POP, RIGHT?

12:30.734 --> 12:32.732
WHO ARE YOU TEXTING?
KAMORA?

12:32.734 --> 12:34.332
NOBODY.
GIMME A SEC.

12:34.334 --> 12:35.898
IT'S<i> YOUR</i> TOUR.

12:35.900 --> 12:38.332
I SHOULDN'T CARE ABOUT IT
MORE THAN YOU DO.

12:38.334 --> 12:39.065
ALL RIGHT.

12:40.400 --> 12:41.532
LET'S SEE.

12:41.534 --> 12:44.865
<i> [ HIP-HOP MUSIC PLAYS ]</i>

12:44.867 --> 12:46.265
OKAY. GREAT!

12:46.267 --> 12:48.065
YEAH. STICK IT UP
ON THE SITE,

12:48.067 --> 12:49.132
AND, UH, BABE,

12:49.134 --> 12:50.998
CAN YOU GET STARTED
ON MY PACKIN'?

12:51.000 --> 12:51.932
YEAH, I'M LATE.

12:53.134 --> 12:54.865
I'M PACKING
YOUR CLOTHES NOW?

12:55.800 --> 12:57.865
I MEAN, YOU KNOW,
JUST LAY OUT A FEW OPTIONS.

12:57.867 --> 12:59.932
H-HOW YOU SAY?
"MAKE IT POP."

12:59.934 --> 13:00.999
[ CHUCKLES ]

13:03.401 --> 13:05.098
I WANT
AN OFFICIAL TITLE.

13:05.100 --> 13:06.232
MY GIRL.

13:06.234 --> 13:07.798
DOESN'T GET ANY MORE
OFFICIAL THAN THAT.

13:07.800 --> 13:09.598
A<i> PAID</i> POSITION.

13:09.600 --> 13:12.032
I'M ALREADY DOING
LIKE 10 JOBS FOR YOU.

13:12.034 --> 13:15.065
IF YOU'RE NOT GONNA LET ME
GO TO SPELMAN OR ANYWHERE,

13:15.067 --> 13:16.265
LET ME GET A JOB.

13:16.267 --> 13:17.398
AS WHAT?

13:17.400 --> 13:19.132
I DON'T KNOW,
A VIDEOGRAPHER?

13:19.134 --> 13:21.465
LET YOUR LABEL PAY ME.

13:21.467 --> 13:23.332
I'LL TALK TO THE LABEL.

13:23.334 --> 13:25.065
THAT'S ALL I WANTED.

13:25.067 --> 13:26.998
NOW START PACKIN'!

13:27.000 --> 13:28.932
YEAH, I HEARD
THAT'S PRIME REAL ESTATE

13:28.934 --> 13:31.065
FOR VIDEOGRAPHERS'
JOB DESCRIPTION --

13:31.067 --> 13:32.632
PACKIN' YOUR MAN.

13:37.267 --> 13:39.031
[ Telephone rings ]
ROCHELLE: Hello?

13:39.033 --> 13:41.331
HEY, ROCHELLE.
IT'S CORALIE HUNTER.

13:41.333 --> 13:42.732
HEY, GIRL.
HOW YOU DOIN'?

13:42.734 --> 13:44.198
My oldest just texted me

13:44.200 --> 13:46.132
the address
of their foster home, Ro.

13:46.134 --> 13:47.865
They want me
to come get 'em.

13:47.867 --> 13:49.932
CORALIE, WE'VE BEEN
THROUGH THIS.

13:49.934 --> 13:50.932
ALL RIGHT?

13:50.934 --> 13:52.065
YOU JUST HAVE TO
WAIT 'TIL

13:52.067 --> 13:53.932
after your
court date, okay?

13:53.934 --> 13:56.465
IF YOU TAKE THOSE KIDS WITHOUT
PERMISSION FROM THE COURTS,

13:56.467 --> 13:57.798
YOU'LL NEVER
SEE 'EM AGAIN.

13:57.800 --> 13:59.932
I'M NOT GONNA WAIT
FOR THE TRIAL.

13:59.934 --> 14:00.932
Since when?!

14:01.933 --> 14:03.665
YOU PROMISED ME.

14:03.667 --> 14:05.532
THEY'RE NOT SAFE
WHERE THEY ARE.

14:05.534 --> 14:07.698
UH, THEY DON'T GIVE ME DETAILS
WHEN THEY CALL,

14:07.700 --> 14:10.965
BUT I CAN TELL IT IS --
IT'S NOT GOOD.

14:10.967 --> 14:13.365
I just want to get them
out of there today and go,

14:13.367 --> 14:15.232
but I need money,

14:15.234 --> 14:16.632
AND I -- I --
I CAN'T ASK GRACE.

14:16.634 --> 14:17.699
SHE DOESN'T UNDERSTAND.

14:18.834 --> 14:20.432
WHERE ARE YOU?

14:20.434 --> 14:21.165
Home.

14:23.300 --> 14:24.265
STAY RIGHT THERE.

14:24.267 --> 14:25.665
[ CAR DOOR OPENS ]

14:25.667 --> 14:26.999
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

14:34.200 --> 14:35.265
[ SIGHS ]

14:35.267 --> 14:36.732
Man: OH.

14:36.734 --> 14:38.265
HEY!
BISHOP.

14:38.267 --> 14:39.265
[ LAUGHS ]

14:39.267 --> 14:40.198
GOD IS<i> SO</i> GOOD.

14:40.200 --> 14:41.865
ALL THE TIME.
<i> ALL</i> THE TIME.

14:41.867 --> 14:42.798
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:43.867 --> 14:46.265
WELL, MOST OF THE TIME,
ANYWAY.

14:47.534 --> 14:50.332
PHILIP DEMARS, HUH?

14:50.334 --> 14:51.798
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:51.800 --> 14:53.998
BISHOP GREENLEAF,
HOW YOU DOING, SIR?

14:54.000 --> 14:55.065
HEY.

14:55.067 --> 14:57.065
HARMONY AND HOPE
MINISTRIES, ISN'T IT?

14:57.067 --> 14:58.065
[ CHUCKLES ]

14:58.067 --> 15:00.232
VERY FUNNY, BISHOP.
VERY FUNNY.

15:00.234 --> 15:02.032
SO...

15:02.034 --> 15:04.231
WHAT BRINGS YOU
TO CALVARY?

15:04.233 --> 15:05.565
I INVITED HIM, JAMES.
YOU REMEMBER.

15:05.567 --> 15:07.398
OH, YES.
CONNIE<i> DID</i> MENTION IT.

15:07.400 --> 15:10.132
HOW IS IT
OVER AT H&H?

15:10.134 --> 15:13.865
WELL, WE HAVE CHURCHES
IN OVER 100 COUNTRIES NOW.

15:13.867 --> 15:15.099
MM.

15:15.101 --> 15:17.765
NEXT STOP,
NORTH KOREA.

15:17.767 --> 15:19.698
WELL,
FINGERS CROSSED.

15:19.700 --> 15:21.199
WELL, THAT'S FANTASTIC.

15:22.234 --> 15:23.532
JUST FANTASTIC.

15:25.000 --> 15:27.831
I'LL LEAVE YOU TWO
TO CONSPIRE.

15:27.833 --> 15:29.299
GOOD SEEING YOU,
JAMES.

15:29.301 --> 15:30.932
AND IT WAS GOOD TO
SEE YOU, TOO, PHIL...

15:31.733 --> 15:32.799
...AND...

15:32.801 --> 15:34.931
IT'S STILL "BISHOP",

15:34.933 --> 15:37.665
AND I DON'T SEE THAT
CHANGING ANYTIME SOON.

15:37.667 --> 15:45.665
♪♪

15:45.667 --> 15:47.098
IF YOU ASK ME...

15:48.467 --> 15:51.199
THAT'S A CHURCH MAN WHO KNOWS
HIS DAYS ARE NUMBERED.

15:52.500 --> 15:54.465
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

15:54.467 --> 15:55.332
[ SCOFFS ]

15:56.734 --> 15:58.865
[ SIGHS ]
EVERYTHING OKAY?

15:58.867 --> 16:01.999
YEAH, JUST...KERISSA
DRIVING ME CRAZY, MAN.

16:05.067 --> 16:07.132
SHE THINKS TASHA'S
IN LOVE WITH ME.

16:10.134 --> 16:12.132
WHY WOULD
SHE THINK THAT?

16:12.134 --> 16:14.132
BECAUSE WE KISSED ONCE.

16:14.134 --> 16:15.465
YOU -- JACOB!

16:15.467 --> 16:16.499
WHAT'D YOU HIT ME FOR?!

16:17.600 --> 16:19.332
MAN, WHEN ARE YOU
GONNA GROW UP?

16:19.334 --> 16:20.932
WHAT DO YOU MEAN,
"GROW UP"?

16:20.934 --> 16:22.198
IT'S BARELY A KISS.

16:22.200 --> 16:23.798
BARELY A KI--
DO YOU LOVE HER?

16:23.800 --> 16:25.865
WHO? TASHA? NO.

16:25.867 --> 16:27.598
YOU STILL LOVE KERISSA?

16:27.600 --> 16:29.065
AFTER ALL THESE YEARS?

16:30.200 --> 16:31.232
I GUESS.

16:33.600 --> 16:35.932
I MEAN, ARE THINGS THE WAY
THEY USED TO BE? NO.

16:35.934 --> 16:37.432
BUT, I MEAN, YOU KNOW...

16:40.667 --> 16:42.365
HOW ARE THINGS
WITH YOU AND DARIUS?

16:43.467 --> 16:46.465
NOT GREAT.
[ SIGHS ]

16:46.467 --> 16:48.032
NOT EVEN<i> GOOD,</i> REALLY.

16:50.400 --> 16:53.132
THAT IS THE LEAST
OF MY PROBLEMS.

16:53.134 --> 16:55.198
KERISSA, THOUGH...

16:55.200 --> 16:56.332
[ SIGHS ]

16:56.334 --> 16:57.332
I MEAN...

16:57.334 --> 16:58.798
YEAH?

16:58.800 --> 17:00.065
I DON'T KNOW.
I -- I -- I...

17:00.067 --> 17:02.998
SOMETIMES I THINK...

17:03.000 --> 17:04.732
YOU KNOW, I WONDER
IF WE EVER<i> DID</i> BREAK UP,

17:04.734 --> 17:07.265
IF...ANYBODY ELSE
WOULD NOTICE

17:07.267 --> 17:09.265
WHAT SHE LOOKS LIKE
WHEN SHE...

17:09.267 --> 17:10.998
WHEN SHE SLEEPS,
YOU KNOW?

17:11.000 --> 17:12.465
[ CHUCKLES ]

17:14.800 --> 17:17.198
I CAN ALWAYS FEEL,
LIKE,

17:17.200 --> 17:19.665
THIS LITTLE BONE
IN HER CHEEK, YOU KNOW,

17:19.667 --> 17:22.165
WHEN I KISS HER
GOOD MORNING.

17:23.734 --> 17:26.465
I FEEL THAT CHEEKBONE...

17:26.467 --> 17:28.398
AGAINST MINE,
AND, UH...

17:28.400 --> 17:30.798
YOU KNOW, I KNOW SHE'S...
IT'S HER.

17:30.800 --> 17:32.732
SHE'S IN THERE.
MM-HMM.

17:32.734 --> 17:34.332
[ VEHICLE APPROACHES ]

17:35.801 --> 17:37.865
YO, YOU SEE THIS?

17:37.867 --> 17:45.799
♪♪

17:45.801 --> 17:47.465
IS THAT TASHA
WITH HER?

17:47.467 --> 17:53.332
♪♪

17:53.334 --> 17:56.132
I TOLD YOU
IT WOULD TAKE A MIRACLE.

17:56.134 --> 17:57.332
WAIT, NO,
NO, NO, WAIT.

17:57.334 --> 18:01.265
♪♪

18:01.267 --> 18:02.932
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

18:02.934 --> 18:04.699
[ Whispering ]
Okay. Let's go.

18:09.734 --> 18:11.665
SO, YOU'RE ROCHELLE'S
SISTER-IN-LAW.

18:12.534 --> 18:13.631
YEAH.

18:13.633 --> 18:15.499
THANK YOU AGAIN
FOR ALL YOUR HELP

18:15.501 --> 18:17.365
WITH THE KIDS
AND EVERYTHING.

18:17.367 --> 18:19.532
OH, NO WORRIES.

18:19.534 --> 18:20.465
I'VE BEEN THERE.

18:21.534 --> 18:23.798
UM, WOULD YOU MIND
IF I USED YOUR PHONE

18:23.800 --> 18:25.132
FOR JUST A QUICK SECOND?
SURE.

18:25.134 --> 18:28.131
TASHA, LET'S NOT
BE RUDE NOW.

18:28.133 --> 18:30.532
WHATEVER BUSINESS YOU GOT,
WE CAN HANDLE IT LATER,

18:30.534 --> 18:32.065
AFTER WE --
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

18:32.900 --> 18:34.899
YOU EXPECTING
SOMEBODY?

18:34.901 --> 18:36.532
DON'T YOU DARE
OPEN THAT DOOR!

18:36.534 --> 18:37.465
I'M SORRY.

18:39.200 --> 18:40.765
JACOB!

18:42.867 --> 18:45.265
AFTER EVERYTHING
I'VE DONE FOR YOU?!

18:45.267 --> 18:46.999
OH, THIS WHITE FOLKS'
RULES, FOR SURE.

18:47.001 --> 18:49.598
GRACE TOLD ME WHAT YOU'VE DONE
TO HER FATHER, TO HER FAMILY.

18:49.600 --> 18:50.631
YOU BELIEVED HER?

18:50.633 --> 18:52.398
I DIDN'T ENTIRELY
AT FIRST,

18:52.400 --> 18:53.798
BUT I DO NOW.

18:53.800 --> 18:54.865
TASHA, LET'S GO.

18:54.867 --> 18:55.532
NO.

18:55.534 --> 18:56.831
WE'RE GETTING
OUTTA HERE!

18:56.833 --> 18:58.631
THESE FOLKS AIN'T YOUR FAMILY.
I AM. LET'S GO!

18:58.633 --> 19:01.765
YOU HAVE BEEN NOTHIN'
BUT TROUBLE FOR ME, ROCHELLE.

19:01.767 --> 19:02.899
AND WHAT
ABOUT BASIE?

19:02.901 --> 19:03.832
WHAT ABOUT HIM?

19:03.834 --> 19:05.298
THE WAY HE SAVED YOU,
TASHA,

19:05.300 --> 19:06.531
LIFTED YOU UP
FROM THE GUTTER --

19:06.533 --> 19:08.265
I SAVED MYSELF
WITH GOD.

19:08.267 --> 19:09.299
SHE BELONGS
TO BASIE.

19:09.301 --> 19:11.132
WELL, SHE'S WITH US NOW,
ROCHELLE.

19:14.567 --> 19:16.065
OKAY. ALL RIGHT.

19:17.301 --> 19:18.232
ROT IN HELL.

19:18.234 --> 19:20.098
Grace: HEY.

19:20.100 --> 19:22.232
YOUR KIDS ARE BETTER OFF
WITH SOMEBODY ELSE.

19:22.234 --> 19:24.398
THEIR MOTHER IS NOTHING BUT A
LYING, LITTLE, MURDERING BITCH!

19:24.400 --> 19:26.699
STOP IT, ROCHELLE!

19:26.701 --> 19:28.565
THIS IS OVER!
LET IT GO!

19:30.367 --> 19:31.499
AT THE END
OF THE DAY...

19:33.567 --> 19:34.898
...YOU'RE NOTHING
LIKE ME.

19:34.900 --> 19:37.465
I KNOW I'M A SINNER
DESERVING OF HELL,

19:37.467 --> 19:40.598
BUT YOU...YOU THINK
YOU'RE SOME DAMN SAINT!

19:40.600 --> 19:42.799
NO, I DON'T.
OH, YES, YOU DO.

19:42.801 --> 19:44.665
YOU THINK YOU'RE
ON THE RIGHT SIDE...

19:45.701 --> 19:48.465
...'CAUSE THAT'S WHAT
HAPPENS WHEN YOU GET ALL
THE MONEY GROWING UP.

19:48.467 --> 19:49.999
IT FOOLS YOU INTO THINKING
YOU'RE ALL RIGHT,

19:50.001 --> 19:52.531
AND YOU'RE NOT.

19:52.533 --> 19:56.598
LET'S SEE WHICH ONE OF
US IS SITTING ON THE RIGHT
SIDE OF GOD ON THAT DAY.

19:56.600 --> 19:57.799
I HOPE WE BOTH ARE.

19:57.801 --> 19:59.765
YOU WHORE!
WHAT'D YOU CALL ME?

19:59.767 --> 20:01.865
I KNOW WHAT YOU DID
IN PHOENIX.

20:01.867 --> 20:06.931
♪♪

20:06.933 --> 20:08.599
[ DOOR OPENS, SLAMS ]

20:10.133 --> 20:11.799
WE GONNA CALL THE FEDS
OR WHAT?

20:14.234 --> 20:15.632
ARE YOU OKAY TO TALK
TO THE FBI TONIGHT?

20:15.634 --> 20:16.831
YEAH.

20:16.833 --> 20:18.232
AND YOU'LL MAKE IT CLEAR
MY FATHER AND MY BROTHER

20:18.234 --> 20:19.498
HAD NOTHING TO DO
WITH ANY OF THIS.

20:19.500 --> 20:20.632
YES.

20:20.634 --> 20:21.765
WE'RE GONNA LET HER
GET AWAY?

20:21.767 --> 20:23.232
JACOB, I DON'T
CARE ABOUT THAT.

20:23.234 --> 20:24.465
I JUST CARE ABOUT
YOU AND DADDY.

20:24.467 --> 20:25.531
LET IT GO.

20:25.533 --> 20:27.432
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

20:27.434 --> 20:30.032
[ SIGHS ] CAN YOU GIVE ME
A MOMENT TO TALK TO CORALIE?

20:31.633 --> 20:33.832
ALL RIGHT. COME ON.
WE'LL WAIT IN THE CAR.

20:33.834 --> 20:36.598
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

20:36.600 --> 20:38.832
YOU'LL TELL THE FBI
I HELPED YOU, RIGHT?

20:38.834 --> 20:41.032
YOU PROMISED YOU WOULD.
OF COURSE I WILL.

20:41.034 --> 20:44.332
WHEN ELLIE INTRODUCES IT
AS EVIDENCE INTO YOUR CASE,

20:44.334 --> 20:47.265
THE JURY'S GONNA KNOW
THAT YOU ARE A GOOD PERSON,

20:47.267 --> 20:48.132
AND YOU ARE.

20:48.134 --> 20:49.798
I DON'T FEEL LIKE ONE
RIGHT NOW.

20:49.800 --> 20:55.998
♪♪

20:56.000 --> 20:57.665
YOU DID
THE RIGHT THING...

20:59.534 --> 21:01.398
...BUT I'M NOT GONNA REST
UNTIL YOU ARE FREE

21:01.400 --> 21:03.332
AND BACK WITH YOUR KIDS
FOR GOOD.

21:03.334 --> 21:05.798
[ SIGHS ]
THANK YOU.

21:05.800 --> 21:16.399
♪♪

21:16.401 --> 21:18.598
TASHA, I'M A MARRIED MAN.

21:18.600 --> 21:20.599
I'M GONNA BE FAITHFUL
TO KERISSA FROM NOW ON.

21:21.934 --> 21:22.899
I KNOW THAT.

21:24.133 --> 21:25.798
WELL, I HOPE THIS
DOESN'T CHANGE ANYTHING.

21:25.800 --> 21:27.532
HOPE YOU'LL STILL...

21:27.534 --> 21:29.065
HELP US CLEAR
THIS WHOLE THING UP.

21:31.200 --> 21:32.799
YEAH.
OF -- OF COURSE.

21:35.600 --> 21:36.332
HEY.

21:36.334 --> 21:38.598
YOU READY
TO TELL THE TRUTH?

21:38.600 --> 21:40.198
YEAH.

21:40.200 --> 21:42.532
LET'S DO IT.
LET'S GO.

21:51.900 --> 21:53.365
HEY, YOU GOT
MY CHARGER?

21:53.367 --> 21:54.598
YEAH, IT'S RIGHT HERE,

21:54.600 --> 21:57.065
AND I PUT MY CUT
FOR THE PROMO IN THERE.

21:57.067 --> 21:58.299
WHY YOU
TELLING<i> ME?</i>

22:00.067 --> 22:01.865
'CAUSE I'M OUT.
I'M LEAVING.

22:01.867 --> 22:03.532
WAIT, WAIT. WHAT?

22:03.534 --> 22:04.565
WE<i> BOTH</i> LEAVIN'.

22:05.601 --> 22:06.665
NO.

22:06.667 --> 22:08.032
I'M GOING BACK
TO MEMPHIS.

22:09.134 --> 22:12.732
I MEAN, I'VE DONE
WHAT YOU ASKED ME TO DO.

22:12.734 --> 22:15.565
I'VE DEALT WITH
THE SIDE-CHICK CRAP.

22:15.567 --> 22:18.798
I'VE BEEN YOUR ASSISTANT,
VIDEOGRAPHER, EDITOR,

22:18.800 --> 22:20.932
GRAPHIC DESIGNER,
MAMA, MAID.

22:20.934 --> 22:23.332
I DIDN'T ASK YOU TO
DO HALF OF THAT STUFF
YOU RUN AROUND DOING.

22:23.334 --> 22:24.798
BECAUSE I WAS BORED.

22:24.800 --> 22:26.899
SO I'M BORING NOW?

22:26.901 --> 22:27.898
THAT IT?

22:27.900 --> 22:29.632
WELL, GUESS WHAT?

22:29.634 --> 22:31.332
YOU'RE PRETTY BORING, TOO.

22:31.334 --> 22:33.365
YOU KNOW WHAT
I'M TALKIN' 'BOUT.

22:33.367 --> 22:34.265
BYE.

22:35.833 --> 22:37.632
OKAY, SEE...

22:37.634 --> 22:38.898
SEE, I NEVER
SHOULD HAVE CAME BACK

22:38.900 --> 22:40.532
FOR YOUR
UNGRATEFUL ASS.

22:42.334 --> 22:44.499
NEVER SHOULD HAVE MESSED
WITH YOU IN THE FIRST PLACE.

22:44.501 --> 22:47.099
SHOULD HAVE STUCK IT IN
YOUR COUSIN LIKE SHE WANTED.

22:51.800 --> 22:53.265
YOU AIN'T GOIN' NOWHERE.

22:53.267 --> 22:54.132
ISAIAH, MOVE.

22:54.134 --> 22:55.198
MAKE ME.

22:55.200 --> 22:57.365
ISAIAH, I SAID MOVE!

22:57.367 --> 22:58.832
[ GRUNTS ]

22:58.834 --> 22:59.865
HUH? HUH?

22:59.867 --> 23:02.165
GET OFF OF ME!
NOW WHAT, HUH?

23:02.167 --> 23:03.232
[ GRUNTS ]

23:06.600 --> 23:09.198
WE'RE ON LIVE, ISAIAH.

23:09.200 --> 23:11.532
NOW LET EVERYONE KNOW YOU'RE
GONNA KEEP AWAY FROM ME

23:11.534 --> 23:13.265
WHILE I WALK OUT
THIS DOOR.

23:13.267 --> 23:17.599
♪♪

23:17.601 --> 23:18.699
[ DOOR SLAMS ]

23:25.134 --> 23:26.732
MAY I?

23:26.734 --> 23:27.998
WELL, MAKE IT QUICK.

23:28.000 --> 23:30.665
I HAVE TO FINISH
THIS SERMON BEFORE TOMORROW.

23:32.267 --> 23:34.932
I JUST --
I JUST HEARD FROM GIGI.

23:34.934 --> 23:37.665
SHE'S WITH TASHA SKANKS,
TALKING WITH THE FBI.

23:37.667 --> 23:39.932
IT LOOKS LIKE THIS IS
A HURDLE WE'VE CLEARED.

23:39.934 --> 23:41.732
YOU MUST BE RELIEVED.

23:41.734 --> 23:43.498
WELL, I WOULD BE...

23:43.500 --> 23:44.765
IF I WASN'T
QUITE SO AWARE

23:44.767 --> 23:46.632
OF ANOTHER,
TALLER ONE AHEAD.

23:47.234 --> 23:48.765
WHAT DID YOU DO NOW,
JAMES?

23:48.767 --> 23:51.298
IT'S NOT ME.
IT'S CONNIE.

23:51.300 --> 23:53.432
SHE'S TALKING
WITH PHILIP DEMARS AGAIN

23:53.434 --> 23:56.065
ABOUT US JOINING
HARMONY AND HOPE.

23:56.067 --> 23:57.865
I'LL SEE
THAT DOESN'T HAPPEN.

23:57.867 --> 24:01.132
HAVE YOUR DAY TOMORROW
AND LEAVE IN A TRAIL OF GLORY.

24:01.134 --> 24:03.565
IF YOU STICK AROUND AND TRY
TO FIGHT ME FOR THIS CHURCH,

24:03.567 --> 24:05.232
IT'LL SEND A MESSAGE
TO THE DEACONS THAT WE'RE --

24:05.234 --> 24:07.065
NEITHER ONE OF US --
FIT TO LEAD.

24:07.067 --> 24:09.199
YOU SEAL MY DAY
TOMORROW...

24:10.534 --> 24:13.065
...WITH A PUBLIC
ANNOUNCEMENT

24:13.067 --> 24:16.365
THAT I HERETOFORE
WILL BE CO-PASTOR.

24:16.367 --> 24:17.698
NO.

24:17.700 --> 24:19.998
I DESERVE THAT POSITION
AS MUCH AS YOU DO, JAMES,

24:20.000 --> 24:21.598
<i> MORE</i> TO BE HONEST.

24:21.600 --> 24:23.765
AND THAT'S WHY
I WON'T DO IT!

24:26.667 --> 24:28.465
FOR MONTHS NOW,

24:28.467 --> 24:32.332
YOU'VE BEEN BEATIN' ME DOWN
WITH YOUR HOLY SUPERIORITY.

24:32.334 --> 24:35.665
WELL, I WILL NOT HAVE
MY SOUL WEIGHED BY YOU.

24:35.667 --> 24:37.665
THAT'S A JOB
FOR SAINT PETER OR JESUS.

24:37.667 --> 24:40.199
YOU...YOU ARE JUST
ANOTHER SINNER.

24:42.400 --> 24:43.832
I KNOW THAT, JAMES.

24:45.367 --> 24:47.698
TELL ME
EVERYTHING YOU DID,

24:47.700 --> 24:49.932
AND YOU TELL ME THAT
IT'S NO BETTER OR WORSE

24:49.934 --> 24:51.665
THAN WHAT I DID.

24:51.667 --> 24:53.332
SAY IT!

24:53.334 --> 25:03.032
♪♪

25:03.034 --> 25:05.365
"PRIDE GOETH
BEFORE A FALL."

25:16.467 --> 25:18.565
[ UPBEAT PIANO MUSIC PLAYS ]

25:20.801 --> 25:22.731
[ LIGHT CHEERS ]

25:22.733 --> 25:26.932
♪♪

25:26.934 --> 25:30.098
[ TEMPO INCREASES ]

25:30.100 --> 25:39.299
♪♪

25:39.301 --> 25:42.865
♪♪

25:42.867 --> 25:44.999
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

25:45.001 --> 25:52.198
♪♪

25:52.200 --> 25:55.798
I WILL BLESS THE LORD
AT ALL TIMES.

25:55.800 --> 25:59.998
HIS PRAISE SHALL CONTINUALLY
BE IN MY MIND.

26:00.000 --> 26:03.865
MY SOUL MAKES ITS BOAST
IN THE LORD.

26:03.867 --> 26:07.532
LET THE HUMBLE HEAR
AND BE GLAD.

26:07.534 --> 26:10.531
OH, MAGNIFY THE LORD WITH ME,

26:10.533 --> 26:15.631
AND LET US EXALT HIS NAME TODAY.

26:15.633 --> 26:24.398
♪♪

26:24.400 --> 26:26.699
♪ A CHANGE ♪

26:28.734 --> 26:33.932
♪ A CHANGE HAS COME OVER ♪

26:33.934 --> 26:39.465
♪ ME ♪

26:39.467 --> 26:42.132
♪ HE CHANGED ♪

26:42.134 --> 26:44.365
♪ HE CHANGED ♪

26:44.367 --> 26:46.232
♪ MY LIFE ♪

26:46.234 --> 26:48.132
♪ MY LIFE ♪

26:48.134 --> 26:51.398
♪ AND NOW ♪

26:51.400 --> 26:55.065
♪ I'M FREE-E-E-E-E ♪

26:55.067 --> 26:56.798
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

26:56.800 --> 26:58.865
♪ HE CHANGED ♪

26:58.867 --> 27:02.631
♪ MY LIFE COMPLETE ♪

27:02.633 --> 27:05.899
♪ AND NOW I SIT ♪

27:05.901 --> 27:11.598
♪ I SIT AT HIS FEET ♪

27:11.600 --> 27:17.965
♪ TO DO
WHAT MUST BE DONE ♪

27:17.967 --> 27:22.265
♪ I'LL WORK AND WORK ♪

27:22.267 --> 27:26.565
♪ UNTIL HE COMES ♪

27:26.567 --> 27:33.232
♪ A WONDERFUL CHANGE ♪

27:33.234 --> 27:38.465
♪ HAS COME OVER ♪

27:38.467 --> 27:41.598
♪ ME ♪

27:41.600 --> 27:44.798
♪ A WONDERFUL ♪

27:44.800 --> 27:46.531
♪ WONDERFUL ♪

27:46.533 --> 27:48.998
♪ CHANGE ♪

27:49.000 --> 27:56.398
♪ HAS COME OVER ME ♪
♪ OH, IT'S ALL OVER ME ♪

27:56.400 --> 28:00.398
♪ LORD, YOU CHANGED ♪

28:00.400 --> 28:02.765
♪ MY LIFE COMPLETE ♪

28:02.767 --> 28:04.565
♪ CHANGE ♪

28:04.567 --> 28:06.198
♪ AND NOW I SIT ♪

28:06.200 --> 28:08.198
♪ CHANGE ♪

28:08.200 --> 28:11.065
♪ I SIT AT HIS FEET ♪

28:11.067 --> 28:12.232
WHOO!

28:14.200 --> 28:17.532
♪ HE CHANGED
THE WAY I WALK ♪

28:17.534 --> 28:22.732
♪ THE WAY
I BE-E-E-E-E-E-E-E ♪

28:22.734 --> 28:24.065
♪ THANK GOD ♪

28:24.067 --> 28:25.499
♪ THANK GOD ♪

28:27.334 --> 28:30.832
♪ I'VE GOT YOU ♪

28:30.834 --> 28:33.565
♪ CHANGE ♪

28:33.567 --> 28:37.365
♪ I'VE BEEN SET FREE ♪

28:37.367 --> 28:39.299
♪ AH-AH ♪

28:39.301 --> 28:41.631
♪ AHHHHH ♪

28:41.633 --> 28:46.232
♪ A WONDERFUL CHANGE ♪

28:46.234 --> 28:49.932
♪ SO GLAD, SO GLAD ♪
♪ HAS COME ♪

28:49.934 --> 28:52.665
♪ I'M GONNA WALK ON
IN HIS GLORY ♪

28:52.667 --> 29:01.465
♪ OVER ME-E-E-E-E-E ♪

29:01.467 --> 29:02.865
♪ YEAH ♪

29:02.867 --> 29:06.298
♪ YEAH ♪
♪ OOOOOOH ♪

29:06.300 --> 29:09.299
♪ HALLELUJAH ♪

29:09.301 --> 29:11.432
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

29:16.201 --> 29:19.365
THANK YOU, LORD!
THANK YOU! THANK YOU!

29:19.367 --> 29:21.099
ALL RIGHT, CHARITY.

29:23.367 --> 29:27.365
I WOULD LIKE FOR CHARITY
TO DO THE HONORS.

29:27.367 --> 29:29.165
OH! YES!

29:29.167 --> 29:32.398
UM...
WELL, WHAT CAN I SAY?

29:32.400 --> 29:35.398
CALVARY, GUESTS,

29:35.400 --> 29:37.665
I CALL HER MAMA.

29:37.667 --> 29:40.332
AND I, STARTING TODAY,

29:40.334 --> 29:42.532
AM CALLING HER
PASTOR GREENLEAF.

29:42.534 --> 29:45.332
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

29:45.334 --> 29:49.198
COME ON OUT HERE,
PASTOR MAE GREENLEAF!

29:49.200 --> 29:51.198
WHOOOOO!

29:51.200 --> 29:54.099
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

30:05.701 --> 30:07.632
[ CELLPHONE VIBRATES ]

30:26.667 --> 30:28.332
HEY, IT'S ME.

30:29.334 --> 30:31.532
I JUST GOT THE RESULTS.

30:31.534 --> 30:33.532
MNH-MNH.
I HAVEN'T OPENED THEM YET.

30:33.534 --> 30:35.099
CAN YOU COME
TO THE CHURCH?

30:35.101 --> 30:38.865
[ MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
ON P.A. ]

30:38.867 --> 30:41.099
[ INDISTINCT CHATTER ]

30:52.600 --> 30:53.999
[ CAR DOOR CLOSES ]

30:54.001 --> 30:55.598
THANKS FOR COMING.

30:55.600 --> 30:57.199
NO WORRIES.

31:00.467 --> 31:01.765
THANKS.

31:02.901 --> 31:04.332
WHERE TO?

31:06.567 --> 31:09.232
[ DISTANT CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

31:09.234 --> 31:11.632
GIGI.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

31:14.667 --> 31:16.398
HEY, DADDY.

31:16.400 --> 31:18.532
HOW'S IT GOIN'
IN THERE?

31:18.534 --> 31:19.732
MM.

31:19.734 --> 31:22.332
IF I HAD TO ANSWER
WITH THE IMPARTIALITY

31:22.334 --> 31:25.998
OF THE JOURNALIST
THAT I ONCE WAS...

31:26.000 --> 31:27.465
EXTRAORDINARILY.

31:27.467 --> 31:29.065
HM.
MM.

31:29.067 --> 31:30.065
WELL...

31:31.400 --> 31:33.099
[ INHALES ]
THANK YOU.

31:34.534 --> 31:36.665
FOR WHAT, DADDY?

31:36.667 --> 31:38.565
[ INHALES ]

31:39.734 --> 31:43.199
I WAS FOOLISH,
AND YOU LOVED ME.

31:45.167 --> 31:49.065
I PUT MYSELF AND THIS WHOLE
FAMILY IN JEOPARDY, AND...

31:49.067 --> 31:52.465
YOU NEVER STOPPED
FIGHTING TO SAVE US ALL...

31:54.467 --> 31:55.765
...AND I THANK YOU.

31:57.034 --> 31:58.899
I LOVE YOU, DADDY.

32:02.534 --> 32:04.398
I KNOW.
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]

32:04.400 --> 32:06.132
[ Voice breaking ]
I KNOW IT.

32:08.934 --> 32:11.365
I TREASURE YOU.

32:11.367 --> 32:14.065
I HAVE NEVER FELT SO...

32:14.067 --> 32:15.332
HUMBLED.

32:16.933 --> 32:21.199
ALL YOU'VE DONE FOR ME,
MY PRECIOUS DAUGHTER...

32:21.201 --> 32:22.465
[ SNIFFLING ]

32:24.400 --> 32:26.998
I THANK YOU.

32:27.000 --> 32:28.332
[ SOBS ]

32:28.334 --> 32:31.798
IF THERE'S ONE THING
I COULD GO BACK AND CHANGE

32:31.800 --> 32:35.265
IN THE PREACHING
THAT I HEARD AS A GIRL,

32:35.267 --> 32:39.932
IT WOULD BE WHAT I HEARD ABOUT
THAT DREADED DAY OF RECKONIN'.

32:39.934 --> 32:41.565
[ SCATTERED APPROVAL ]

32:41.567 --> 32:45.832
THAT DREADED DAY WHEN THE DEAD
WOULD RISE UP FROM THE GRAVE.

32:45.834 --> 32:47.032
YOU REMEMBER, DON'T YOU?

32:47.034 --> 32:48.565
Audience: YES!

32:48.567 --> 32:53.065
YES, AND EVERY SOUL WAS GONNA
GET WHAT THEY DESERVED.

32:53.067 --> 32:55.332
YES!     YEAH!    YES!     YEAH!

32:55.334 --> 32:57.998
I MEAN, HERE I AM...

32:58.000 --> 33:02.899
A LITTLE, BITTY, PRECIOUS
BABY GIRL,

33:02.901 --> 33:06.099
AND I JUST KNEW I HAD SINNED.

33:06.101 --> 33:07.632
I DON'T KNOW --
MUST HAVE BEEN

33:07.634 --> 33:10.032
THAT CHOCOLATE-CHIP COOKIE
I TOOK OUT OF THE KITCHEN,

33:10.034 --> 33:13.799
BUT I<i> KNEW...</i>
THAT I HAD SINNED.

33:16.067 --> 33:18.865
IF I COULD JUST GO BACK

33:18.867 --> 33:25.398
AND JUST PUT
SOME SMALL MEASURE OF TENDERNESS

33:25.400 --> 33:30.798
IN THE HEARTS OF THOSE MEN
WHO WERE PREACHING TO ME --

33:30.800 --> 33:36.198
SOME SMALL DROP OF WISDOM
IN THEIR MINDS

33:36.200 --> 33:40.099
SO THAT THEY MIGHT HAVE
ENCOURAGED ME.

33:40.101 --> 33:41.899
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

33:41.901 --> 33:42.899
OH...

33:44.534 --> 33:46.265
HOW I WISHED

33:46.267 --> 33:52.465
THAT THEY HAD FILLED ME...
WITH THE<i> CONFIDENCE...</i>

33:52.467 --> 33:56.431
THAT JESUS BOUGHT AND PAID FOR
ON THAT CROSS!

33:56.433 --> 34:01.332
YES! SO THAT ON THAT DAY
OF THAT GREAT RECKONING,

34:01.334 --> 34:06.065
I<i> REALLY</i> WOULD HAVE GOTTEN
ALL THAT I DESERVED,

34:06.067 --> 34:09.932
WHICH IS THE UNDYING LOVE
OF MY LORD!

34:09.934 --> 34:12.565
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

34:12.567 --> 34:18.232
AND WE ARE GOING
TO REPLACE ALL THAT FEAR...

34:19.700 --> 34:21.498
...WITH LOVE.

34:21.500 --> 34:23.665
[ CHEERING ]

34:23.667 --> 34:25.265
LOVE!

34:28.067 --> 34:30.065
HEY, YOU GOT A SECOND?

34:30.067 --> 34:31.232
FOR WHAT?

34:33.800 --> 34:35.698
WOULD YOU LOOK AT ME,
PLEASE?

34:35.700 --> 34:36.999
WHAT?

34:43.267 --> 34:44.565
I LOVE YOU.

34:46.067 --> 34:47.999
I KNOW.
NO. I MEAN IT, KEE.

34:49.134 --> 34:50.132
I LOVE YOU.

34:51.834 --> 34:54.598
I WAS TALKING WITH
GIGI LAST NIGHT, AND...

34:54.600 --> 34:55.899
AND I REALIZED...

34:57.534 --> 34:58.665
...I LOVE YOU.

35:00.300 --> 35:02.032
YOU REALIZED IT?

35:02.034 --> 35:03.165
YEAH.

35:04.367 --> 35:05.532
JACOB.

35:09.733 --> 35:13.132
IF YOU JUST TAKE THIS BOOK UP
AND READ IT,

35:13.134 --> 35:16.865
YOU CANNOT NOT KNOW
THAT GOD LOVES YOU.

35:16.867 --> 35:18.232
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

35:18.234 --> 35:20.798
OH, IT'S ALL
THROUGH THIS BOOK,

35:20.800 --> 35:25.698
AND IF YOU READ THIS BOOK
AND YOU FEEL UNLOVED,

35:25.700 --> 35:27.465
SATAN HAS INTERVENED.

35:27.467 --> 35:30.265
AMEN! HALLELUJAH!

35:30.267 --> 35:34.065
LADIES, YOU KNOW IN SOME
OF OUR TROUBLED NEIGHBORHOODS,

35:34.067 --> 35:38.332
EVERY SUMMER, WE HAVE THAT
"TAKE BACK THE NIGHT."

35:38.334 --> 35:40.465
WELL, SISTERS,
LET ME TELL YOU SOMETHIN'.

35:40.467 --> 35:43.132
TODAY, YOU KNOW WHAT WE DOIN'?

35:43.134 --> 35:46.465
WE ARE GOING
TO TAKE BACK THE<i> LIGHT.</i>

35:46.467 --> 35:50.065
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

35:50.067 --> 35:53.132
[ CHEERING FADES ]

35:53.134 --> 35:54.432
[ DOOR OPENS ]

35:57.700 --> 35:59.698
JUST THOUGHT
I'D COME BY TO GIVE YOU

35:59.700 --> 36:01.765
WHAT GOD
IS TOO SELFISH TO GIVE.

36:08.434 --> 36:10.965
James: SON, DON'T DO THIS.
YOU THINK I WANT TO, OLD MAN?

36:10.967 --> 36:13.065
ALL I WANTED WAS TO SHUT
YOU DOWN, OLD MAN,

36:13.067 --> 36:15.299
TEACH YOU A LESSON, BUT YOU
GOT SOMETHIN', I DON'T KNOW,

36:15.301 --> 36:17.765
SATAN OR SOMEBODY --
DEMONS PROTECTING YOU.

36:17.767 --> 36:19.332
NO, THIS IS YOUR FAULT.

36:19.334 --> 36:21.765
THE ONLY WAY TO STOP YOU
IS TO KILL YOU DEAD.

36:21.767 --> 36:24.065
SON...
I'M NOT YOUR SON, BOY!

36:24.067 --> 36:27.598
WE REALLY DON'T...
HAVE TO LOOK.

36:27.600 --> 36:28.732
WE DO.

36:28.734 --> 36:30.099
<i> I</i> DO.

36:31.867 --> 36:34.332
[ Sighing ]
GOSH, I...

36:34.334 --> 36:36.998
GUESS I'M MORE LIKE
THESE PEOPLE THAN I THOUGHT.

36:37.000 --> 36:38.265
HOW SO?

36:39.601 --> 36:41.731
[ CHUCKLES ]
I'M ALWAYS GIVING EVERYONE

36:41.733 --> 36:44.598
SUCH A HARD TIME FOR NOT
FACING UP TO THE TRUTH,

36:44.600 --> 36:47.132
BUT I WON'T FACE<i> THIS.</i>

36:47.134 --> 36:49.865
YOU KNOW, IT MIGHT NOT BE
WHAT YOU THINK IT IS.

36:49.867 --> 36:51.198
AND IF IT IS?

36:51.200 --> 36:53.098
I'M TELLING YOU THIS OUT OF
NOTHIN' BUT LOVE FOR YOU.

36:53.100 --> 36:54.198
LOVE?
DON'T!

36:54.200 --> 36:57.431
YOU KILLED MY DADDY!
I DIDN'T MEAN TO DO IT!

36:57.433 --> 36:59.265
NOW THE TRUTH
IS COMIN' OUT.

36:59.267 --> 37:00.532
IF YOU SHOOT ME...

37:00.534 --> 37:01.799
MM-HMM.

37:03.600 --> 37:05.932
...IT'LL BE TWO LIVES
I'VE TAKEN.

37:05.934 --> 37:08.432
I'D HAVE MADE YOU
A MURDERER,

37:08.434 --> 37:11.032
AND YOUR LIFE, WHAT'S LEFT
OF IT, WILL BE OVER.

37:11.034 --> 37:12.265
GET AWAY!

37:12.267 --> 37:13.299
GET AWAY!

37:14.600 --> 37:16.498
IT'S NOT JUST ABOUT ME.

37:16.500 --> 37:18.398
TO SEE THAT LIGHT
IN MY FATHER'S EYES

37:18.400 --> 37:23.031
THAT'S BEEN THERE SINCE THE DAY
THAT I WAS BORN FADE AWAY,

37:23.033 --> 37:25.598
I HATE THAT MY MOTHER HAS
PUT US BOTH IN THIS POSITION --

37:25.600 --> 37:27.932
TO LOSE SO MUCH
ALL AT ONCE.

37:29.800 --> 37:31.265
GRACE, I MEAN IT.

37:32.600 --> 37:34.065
WE REALLY
DON'T HAVE TO --

37:38.667 --> 37:40.531
YOU'VE LOST YOUR CHURCH...

37:40.533 --> 37:43.598
YOU LOST YOUR WIFE...

37:43.600 --> 37:44.898
AND NOW YOU'VE LOST
YOUR SOUL.

37:44.900 --> 37:45.898
SHUT UP.

37:45.900 --> 37:48.398
ALL FOR WHAT?
TO MAKE ME PAY...

37:48.400 --> 37:49.598
MM-HMM.

37:49.600 --> 37:50.732
...TO METE OUT JUSTICE,

37:50.734 --> 37:53.799
THE JOB YOU KNOW FULL WELL
IS THE LORD'S ALONE?

37:53.801 --> 37:56.298
NO, YOU GOT TO PAY.
YOU DON'T HAVE TO...

37:56.300 --> 37:58.632
NOT ANY MORE
THAN YOU ALREADY HAVE.

38:00.900 --> 38:03.198
AND I'VE GOT
TO TELL YOU SOMETHING

38:03.200 --> 38:06.198
ABOUT MY SISTER
RIGHT HERE.

38:06.200 --> 38:08.865
ARE WE NOT SO GRATEFUL

38:08.867 --> 38:13.065
TO HAVE MAXINE PATTERSON
IN THE HOUSE? AREN'T WE?

38:13.067 --> 38:15.898
OH, SHE'S BEEN
SO SUPPORTIVE AND SO KIND,

38:15.900 --> 38:18.465
AND YOU KNOW
WHAT SHE TOLD ME?

38:18.467 --> 38:23.998
SHE TOLD ME, "THE TRUTH
WILL SET YOU FREE."

38:24.000 --> 38:25.598
THAT'S WHAT
I TOLD YOU, MAE.

38:25.600 --> 38:26.898
DIDN'T YOU?
YES, I DID.

38:26.900 --> 38:30.199
TO HAVE TO LIVE WITH THOSE
QUESTIONS EVERY DAY, JACOB...

38:31.334 --> 38:34.998
[ Voice breaking ]
"WHY AM I NOT ENOUGH FOR HIM?

38:35.000 --> 38:38.065
WHAT'S WRONG WITH<i> ME?</i>

38:38.067 --> 38:42.065
WHY WOULD HE EVEN
PICK ME IF HE DIDN'T
EVEN REALLY WANT ME?"

38:42.067 --> 38:44.198
KERISSA, YOU<i> ARE</i> ENOUGH.

38:44.200 --> 38:46.665
ALL RIGHT, THERE'S NOTHING
THE MATTER WITH YOU,

38:46.667 --> 38:49.465
AND YOU'RE ALL I WANT.
I KNOW THAT NOW.

38:49.467 --> 38:50.465
IT'S TOO LATE.

38:50.467 --> 38:53.298
PLEASE DON'T DO THIS.
I DON'T HAVE ANY CHOICE.

38:53.300 --> 38:55.465
I JUST WANT
THE PAIN TO STOP.

38:55.467 --> 38:57.732
IT HAS TO END.

38:57.734 --> 38:58.999
THAT'S RIGHT.

38:59.001 --> 39:00.598
OH, MY.

39:00.600 --> 39:03.132
AND IF YOU REALLY WANT
TO CHANGE EVERYTHING...

39:04.534 --> 39:06.865
...YOU GOT TO START
WITH THE TRUTH.

39:06.867 --> 39:07.998
YES!

39:08.000 --> 39:09.398
[ CHEERS AND APPLAUSE ]

39:09.400 --> 39:14.232
START WITH THE TRUTH
AND WALK IN LOVE AND FAITH...

39:16.200 --> 39:19.432
...AND THE CHANGE
WILL TAKE CARE OF ITSELF.

39:21.067 --> 39:23.799
I WANT A DIVORCE, JACOB.

39:23.801 --> 39:26.065
[ DOOR UNLOCKING, OPENS ]

39:43.134 --> 39:44.599
[ SNIFFLING ]

39:48.201 --> 39:50.798
ALL YOU ARE IS A MAN...

39:50.800 --> 39:52.465
WITH A BROKEN HEART...

39:54.133 --> 39:56.398
...AND DEBTS TO PAY.

39:56.400 --> 39:57.799
IF YOU PULL THAT TRIGGER,

39:57.801 --> 40:00.798
YOU'LL SPEND THE REST
OF YOUR LIFE BEHIND BARS.

40:00.800 --> 40:02.465
NO.

40:02.467 --> 40:04.065
THEY NOT GONNA
CATCH<i> ME.</i>

40:04.067 --> 40:06.199
BUT YOU'LL
CATCH YOURSELF!

40:06.201 --> 40:09.332
YOU'LL LOOK IN THAT MIRROR
AND YOU'LL SEE THE THIEF

40:09.334 --> 40:12.865
THAT STOLE THE JOY OF EVERY
MOMENT OF YOUR LIFE.

40:16.167 --> 40:18.099
<i> I</i> SEE HIM EVERY DAY.

40:20.434 --> 40:22.165
NOW, YOU GIVE ME THAT GUN.

40:22.167 --> 40:23.632
DON'T COME ANY CLOSER.

40:25.000 --> 40:27.831
GIVE ME THE GUN.
I SAID, "DON'T COME ANY CLOSER."

40:27.833 --> 40:28.899
GIVE ME THE GUN.

40:28.901 --> 40:30.932
I SAID,
"DON'T COME ANY CLOSER"!

40:32.634 --> 40:35.798
THE DAY OF RECKONING...

40:35.800 --> 40:37.065
IS TODAY.

40:42.234 --> 40:43.665
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

40:46.900 --> 40:49.865
THE DAY OF RECKONING IS TODAY.

40:52.067 --> 40:54.798
GOD'S GREAT DAY OF RECKONING

40:54.800 --> 40:59.465
IS ANY DAY
THAT YOU STEP OUT ON FAITH,

40:59.467 --> 41:04.365
SAY, "THANK YOU, JESUS,"
AND TAKE WHAT'S YOURS

41:04.367 --> 41:08.865
BECAUSE THE DAY
OF RECKONING IS...

41:08.867 --> 41:10.465
TODAY.

41:10.467 --> 41:13.532
YOU'RE A MAN OF GOD,
BASIE.

41:13.534 --> 41:15.865
UNDER ALL THE PAIN
AND VENGEFUL FEELINGS,

41:15.867 --> 41:17.665
YOU ARE A MAN OF GOD.
MMMM.

41:17.667 --> 41:20.865
NO ONE COULD PREACH LIKE YOU
WITHOUT KNOWING THAT GOD,

41:20.867 --> 41:22.731
GOD IS GOD,

41:22.733 --> 41:24.332
WITHOUT KNOWING
WHAT LIFE IS.

41:24.334 --> 41:26.032
YOU KNOW.

41:32.067 --> 41:33.998
